containerId": null, "originalText": "purge", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "rect-0175", "x": 1130, "y": 110, "width": 480, "height": 840, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 176007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2301, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "rectangle"}, {"id": "txt-0178", "x": 1150, "y": 128, "width": 113.1, "height": 18, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 179007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2340, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "CAPACITY MATH", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "CAPACITY MATH", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0181", "x": 1150, "y": 154, "width": 384.25, "height": 93, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 182007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2379, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 12.5, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "Messages: 500 DAU x 20 = 10k/day = 0.12 msg/s avg\nPeak (x50 burst): ~6-10 msg/s  ->  trivial for 1 node\nBandwidth: 50 conns x 10 KB/s = 500 KB/s (~4 Mbps)\nStorage: 10 MB/day text -> 3.7 GB/yr, but 30d\nretention keeps hot set at ~300 MB (+ media in MinIO)\nFits on: ONE Coolify server (4 vCPU / 8 GB)", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "Messages: 500 DAU x 20 = 10k/day = 0.12 msg/s avg\nPeak (x50 burst): ~6-10 msg/s  ->  trivial for 1 node\nBandwidth: 50 conns x 10 KB/s = 500 KB/s (~4 Mbps)\nStorage: 10 MB/day text -> 3.7 GB/yr, but 30d\nretention keeps hot set at ~300 MB (+ media in MinIO)\nFits on: ONE Coolify server (4 vCPU / 8 GB)", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0184", "x": 1150, "y": 288, "width": 252.29999999999998, "height": 18, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 185007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2418, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "DELIVERY FLOW (at-least-once)", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "DELIVERY FLOW (at-least-once)", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0187", "x": 1150, "y": 314, "width": 384.25, "height": 109, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 188007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2457, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 12.5, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "1. client sends w/ UUID  ->  gateway  ->  msg service\n2. persist to Postgres FIRST, then ack SENT\n3. recipient online?  pub/sub  ->  gateway  ->  push\n   offline?  Redis Stream inbox + FCM notify\n4. device ack -> DELIVERED;  read event -> READ\n5. client dedupes by UUID (retries are safe)\nOrdering: per-chat sequence no. from DB insert", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. client sends w/ UUID  ->  gateway  ->  msg service\n2. persist to Postgres FIRST, then ack SENT\n3. recipient online?  pub/sub  ->  gateway  ->  push\n   offline?  Redis Stream inbox + FCM notify\n4. device ack -> DELIVERED;  read event -> READ\n5. client dedupes by UUID (retries are safe)\nOrdering: per-chat sequence no. from DB insert", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0190", "x": 1150, "y": 460, "width": 348.0, "height": 18, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 191007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2496, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "CONFIGURED IN COOLIFY (no extra tooling)", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "CONFIGURED IN COOLIFY (no extra tooling)", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0193", "x": 1150, "y": 486, "width": 398.75, "height": 125, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 194007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2535, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 12.5, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "- TLS certs: automatic via Traefik + Let's Encrypt\n- sticky WS: one Traefik label on ws-gateway\n- secrets/env: Coolify env vars (shared + per-svc)\n- deploys: GitHub webhook -> build -> rolling restart\n- health checks: per-service, gate the rollout\n- DB backups: scheduled, shipped to S3-compatible\n- retention purge: Scheduled Task on the app\n- alerts: Coolify notifications (Telegram/Discord/mail)", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "- TLS certs: automatic via Traefik + Let's Encrypt\n- sticky WS: one Traefik label on ws-gateway\n- secrets/env: Coolify env vars (shared + per-svc)\n- deploys: GitHub webhook -> build -> rolling restart\n- health checks: per-service, gate the rollout\n- DB backups: scheduled, shipped to S3-compatible\n- retention purge: Scheduled Task on the app\n- alerts: Coolify notifications (Telegram/Discord/mail)", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0196", "x": 1150, "y": 656, "width": 87.0, "height": 18, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 197007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2574, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "RESILIENCE", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "RESILIENCE", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0199", "x": 1150, "y": 682, "width": 355.25, "height": 109, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 200007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2613, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 12.5, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "- 2 gateway replicas; client auto-reconnect w/\n  backoff + resume from last seq no.\n- Redis AOF: offline queue survives restarts\n- Postgres: frequent Coolify backups (no managed\n  replica at this scale; add a 2nd Coolify server\n  + streaming replica when uptime demands it)\n- proxy health checks drop dead containers", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "- 2 gateway replicas; client auto-reconnect w/\n  backoff + resume from last seq no.\n- Redis AOF: offline queue survives restarts\n- Postgres: frequent Coolify backups (no managed\n  replica at this scale; add a 2nd Coolify server\n  + streaming replica when uptime demands it)\n- proxy health checks drop dead containers", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0202", "x": 1150, "y": 830, "width": 226.2, "height": 18, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 203007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2652, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "WHAT WE SKIP AT THIS SCALE", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "WHAT WE SKIP AT THIS SCALE", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "txt-0205", "x": 1150, "y": 856, "width": 362.5, "height": 46, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 206007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2691, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "type": "text", "fontSize": 12.5, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "Kafka, sharding, service mesh, multi-region, k8s.\nCoolify multi-server support covers the next 100x:\nmove data to a 2nd server, scale app replicas.", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "Kafka, sharding, service mesh, multi-region, k8s.\nCoolify multi-server support covers the next 100x:\nmove data to a 2nd server, scale app replicas.", "lineHeight": 1.25}], "appState": {"gridSize": null, "viewBackgroundColor": "#f8f9fb"}, "files": {}}